quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  19,59,"Ngakho-ke emva kwabo kwabe sekufika inzalo eyayingawunaki umthandazo futhi eyayilandela izifiso, iyohlangana nokubhubha esihogweni"
  19,60,Ngaphandle kwalabo abazisolayo futhi bakholwe benze nezenzo ezilungileyo ngakho-ke labo bayongena esivandeni futhi angeke benziwele ngisho nakancane okungeyisibona ubulungiswa
  19,61,Izivande zaphakade okuyizona onomusa azethembisa izinceku zakhe kokungabonwayo ngempela isethembiso sakhe siyagcwaliseka ngasosonke isikhathi
  19,62,Lapho phakathi (ezivandeni) angeke bayizwe inkulumo eyilize kuphela kuyoba ukuthula futhi okwabo kuyoba izipho zabo (izabelo zabo) ekuseni nakusihlwa
  19,63,"Lelo izulu okuyilona esiyokwenza ukuthi izinceku zethu zilithathe njengefa, lezo ezazenza izenzo ezilungileyo"
  19,64,Futhi uGabriyeli wathi asehleli phansi ngaphandle kwempoqo yeNkosi yakho kungokwayo konke lokho okungaphambili kwethu nokungemumva kwethu nokuphakathi kwalokho futhi ngasosonke isikhathi iNkosi yakho ayikhohlwa
  19,65,"INkosi yamazulu nomhlaba nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ngakho-ke yikhonze futhi ube nokubekezele ekuyikhonzeni, ngakube ukhona yini omaziyo ofana nayo na"
  19,66,"Futhi umuntu uthi, “ngakube uma sengifile ngempela ngiyovuswa ngiphila yini na?”"
  19,67,Ngakube umuntu akakhumbuli yini ukuthi thina samdala ngaphambilini kulapho wayengeyilutho na
  19,68,Ngakho-ke ngifunga ngeNkosi yakho ngempela siyobaqoqela ndawonye kanye nabosathane bese sibenza ukuthi babekhona bazungeleze isihogo bekhasa ngamadolo
  19,69,Bese ngempela sikhipha kulelo naleloqembu bonke labo ababephikisana ngokwedlulele nonomusa (uMvelinqangi)
  19,70,Bese ngempela thina sazi kabanzi ngalabo abafaneleke ngokwedlulele ukuba bashiswe kusona (isihogo)
  19,71,"Futhi akekho phakathi kwenu ongeke adlule kusona (isihogo), isidingo eNkosini yakho ekufanele ukuba sifezwe"
  19,72,Ngakho-ke siyosindisa labo ababemesaba uMvelinqangi bese sishiya izoni lapho phakathi zikhasa ngamadolo
  19,73,"Futhi uma befundelwa amavesi ethu acacile bathi labo abangakholwanga kulabo abakholwayo,“yiliphi lamaqembu amabili elingcono ngendawo yokuhlala nelinendawo yokuhlanganela enhle ngokwedlulele na?”"
  19,74,"Futhi zingaki izizukulwane esazibhubhisa ngaphambilini kwabo, zona zazingcono ngokwedlulele ngengcebo nokubukeka"
  19,75,Ithi noma ngabe ubani osekudukeni ngakho-ke onomusa (uMvelinqangi) uzomelulela (intambo) kuze kube ilapho bebona khona lokho ababekuthenjisiwe isijeziso noma ihora ngakho-ke bayokwazi ukuthi ngubani lowo osendaweni embi nokuthi ngeliphi ibutho elibuthakathaka ngokwedlulele”
  19,76,Futhi uMvelinqangi uyabandisa labo abaholiweyo ukuholwa futhi ihlala ikhona imisebenzi emihle ingcono eNkosini yakho mayelana nomvuzo futhi ingcono mayelana nembuyiselo
  19,77,"Ngakube umbonile yini lowo ongakholelwanga emavesini ethu na? Bese ethi, “ngempela ngizophiwa ingcebo nezingane”"
  19,78,Ngakube uyakwazi yini okungabonwayo noma uthathe isivumelwano konomusa na
  19,79,Lutho! Siyokubhala phansi konke lokho akushoyo futhi siyomenyusela isijeziso
  19,80,"Futhi siyokudla ifa, konke lokho akushoyo futhi uyoza kuthina eyedwa"
  19,81,Futhi bathatha izithixo (ukuba bazikhonze) esikhundleni sikaMvelinqangi ukuze zibanike amandla
  19,82,Lutho! (Izithixo) ziyokuphika ukubakhonza kwabo futhi bese ziba yizitha zabo
  19,83,Awuboniyiniukuthisabathumelaosathanekwabangakholwayo ukuze babaphushele ekoneni
  19,84,Ngakho-ke ungabajahi kuphela sibabalela isibalo (sesikhathi esisele)
  19,85,"Ngosuku\tesiyobaqoqela\tngalo\tkonomusa\tlabo\tabenze okulungileyo njengezithunywa"
  19,86,Futhi izoni siyoziholela esihogweni zisesimweni sokunxanwa
  19,87,"Angeke\tbakwazi\tukuzincengela\tngaphandle\tkwalowo owathatha isivumelwano konomusa"
  19,88,"Futhi bathi, “onomusa (uMvelinqangi) unendodana”"
  19,89,Ngempela nilethe into eshaqisayo
  19,90,Amazulu angacishe adabuke ngenxa yalokho nomhlaba udabuke phakathi nezintaba zibhidlike zibe yizicucu
  19,91,(Ngenxa) yokuthi bapha onomusa (uMvelinqangi) indodana (enguJesu)
  19,92,Futhi akumfanele onomusa ukuthi angaba nendodana
  19,93,Akukho ngisho noyedwa osemazulwini nasemhlabeni ngaphandle kokuthi eze konomusa njengenceku
  19,94,Ngempela uyabazi bonke futhi ubabalile isibalo esiphelele
  19,95,Futhi bonke bayoza kuyena ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo bengabodwana
  19,96,Ngempela labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezilungileyo onomusa uyobabekela uthando
  19,97,"Ngakho-ke sikwenze kwalula ngolimi lwakho ukuthi ubatshele ngalo izindaba ezimnandi labo abenza okulungileyo, nokuthi ubaxwayise ngalo abantu abaqhelelene neqiniso"
  19,98,Futhi zingaki izizukulwane esazibhubhisa ngaphambilini kwabo na? Ungamthola yini ngisho noyedwa wabo noma uzwe ubuswebeswebe babo na